{"tid":893833,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發覺自己有「刺激耐受性」？","createTime":"2018-11-08T02:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T05:23:01.000Z","uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0546079043634f3a4b80375d24c096a31b9812","tid":893833,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"依家娛樂真係太多<br />\n日頭飲咖啡，飲茶，刺激個腦有開心幸福既感覺<br />\n期間玩手機game 升lv，上連登食花生笑到賴屎<br />\n夜晚就飲酒飲到wing wing 地進入另一個世界<br />\n再去m記買個餐加大配shake shake 薯條做宵夜<br />\n食完個宵夜再上網搵套AV 打返個 J <br />\n呢d 生活真係爽到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過日子耐左<br />\n會有「刺激耐受性」<br />\n唔再覺得好刺激，只係覺得「... okay la .. 普通啦」 <br />\n但一失去晒以上既刺激<br />\n會突然抑鬱depressed <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427cb35d854c067b6ccb1f5cb50698141692fea1","tid":893833,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:55:17.000Z","msg":"冇人叫您日日咁做"},{"pid":"9f30c22f96a60002d3942698092a1aceb7f6264a","tid":893833,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:56:43.000Z","msg":"所以d 越玩得癲既人<br />\n越容易有抑鬱depression <br />\n因為一冇晒d 刺激就會有withdraw symptoms"},{"pid":"7400396c1c0117583267a2aff6c51de3c957399d","tid":893833,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"打少d飛機啦"},{"pid":"74fb1d96acb644d91d1864a966375781a8884291","tid":893833,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"做gym都係 一開頭既酸痛感覺帶黎快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後已經唔會再有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b457bc4a8e06e92a0fbd07103de5197fafcd9b","tid":893833,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"依個真"},{"pid":"8abc8599e414f238b1be29659ee3e97dc49bc91d","tid":893833,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT